{"id":5966,"type":4,"name":"Fable","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/95/c8/5966_n70mI.jpg","rating":{"total":70,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":0,"4":0,"5":2,"6":6,"7":16,"8":32,"9":13,"10":0},"score":7.6},"summary":"神鬼寓言：失落之章（Fable: The Lost Chapters）是Lionhead Studios于2005年制作完成的一款XBOX上的单机游戏。这个游戏是接续前作——神鬼寓言（Fable）后续剧情的一个动作角色扮演游戏。而之后，这个游戏也先后发行了其PC版本和Mac版本。于2008年，本游戏系列更发展出了第二集——神鬼寓言Ⅱ（Fable II）。\r\n这个游戏运行在一个虚拟的世界“阿尔比恩”中。游戏中的主角是一个孤儿，玩家必须操控他，来实现他成为英雄的梦想。玩家在游戏中做的抉择会影响到这个角色的观念、思想以及反应，也可以选择让其成为一个正义的或邪恶的英雄。在游戏中，玩家可以透过执行任务来一步步的了解到主角的家庭，亦可以透过一些选择性的任务来获得声望、经验值或金钱，并与游戏中的其他人物进行沟通、交易、偷窃或爱情关系。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>神鬼寓言</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/21136\">Lionhead Studios</a>＆Big Blue Box Studios</li><li><span>发行: </span>Microsoft Game Studios、<a href=\"/person/16859\">Xbox Game Studios</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Fable: The Lost Chapter</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>神鬼寓言: 失落之章</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>寓言</li><li><span>平台: </span>Xbox</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>ARPG</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2004年9月14日</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>https://www.microsoft.com/taiwan/games/pc/fable.aspx</li><li><span>游戏设计师: </span>Peter Molyneux</li>","collection":{"wish":14,"collect":87,"doing":2,"on_hold":7,"dropped":5},"tags":[{"name":"RPG","count":18},{"name":"PC","count":17},{"name":"神鬼寓言","count":14},{"name":"狮头社","count":9},{"name":"ARPG","count":9},{"name":"奇幻","count":8},{"name":"欧美系","count":3},{"name":"STEAM","count":2},{"name":"童年","count":2},{"name":"LionheadStudios","count":1},{"name":"普通游戏","count":1},{"name":"2004","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":21136,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/57/dd/21136_prsn_992IA.jpg","name":"狮子头工作室","desc":"开发"},{"id":16859,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/bb/cd/16859_prsn_48aP4.jpg","name":"Xbox游戏工作室","desc":"发行"}],"relations":[{"id":676,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/dc/6a/676_aus.jpg","title":"Fable 2"